## What Was Done

### Goal
Connect the "Listing QuickStart" wizard (publicly accessible at `/onboard/connect`) to real backend property creation in Supabase, then add deduplication, approval flow, clean property IDs, and archive policy.

### Summary of All Changes

| Area | Change | Status |
|------|--------|--------|
| **Airbnb URL Parser** | New API route that uses Playwright to extract listing data | Deployed, tested |
| **Property Onboarding API** | New API route that creates properties in Supabase | Rewritten twice |
| **Wizard UI** | Wired to real backend instead of Formspree-only | Modified |
| **Deduplication** | DB constraints + API check + conflict UI | Active |
| **Clean Property IDs** | Prefix-based (DOM-001) with sequence table | Active |
| **Approval Flow** | Status column (pending/approved/archived/rejected) | DB done, UI partial |
