## Files Modified or Created

### 1. [NEW] [/app/api/listing/extract/route.ts](file:///Users/clawadmin/Antigravity%20Proj/ihouse-core/ihouse-ui/app/api/listing/extract/route.ts)
- **Purpose:** Server-side Airbnb URL parser using Playwright
- **What it does:** Takes a URL, launches headless Chromium, extracts 10 fields with confidence levels
- **Risk:** Playwright dependency was added to [package.json](file:///Users/clawadmin/Antigravity%20Proj/ihouse-core/ihouse-ui/package.json)
- **Size:** ~235 lines

### 2. [REWRITTEN] [/app/api/onboard/route.ts](file:///Users/clawadmin/Antigravity%20Proj/ihouse-core/ihouse-ui/app/api/onboard/route.ts)
- **Purpose:** Property onboarding endpoint — creates properties + channel_map in Supabase
- **Original state:** Non-existent before this session (was Formspree-only)
- **Current state:** Fully rewritten with:
  - Clean ID generation from `tenant_property_config` table
  - `status = 'pending'` on all new properties
  - Dedup check: returns 409 if `source_url` already exists for tenant
  - Status-aware conflict messages (pending/archived/rejected/approved)
  - Formspree notification as backup
  - No `force` override — duplicates are hard-blocked
- **Hardcoded values:** Contains `SUPABASE_URL` and `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` inline
- **Size:** ~170 lines

### 3. [MODIFIED] `/app/(public)/onboard/connect/page.tsx`
- **Purpose:** The Listing QuickStart wizard UI
- **Changes made:**
  - Replaced `simulateImport` with `runImport` calling `/api/listing/extract`
  - Added `extracting`, `extractError`, `conflictProperty` state variables
  - Updated [handleSubmit](file:///Users/clawadmin/Antigravity%20Proj/ihouse-core/ihouse-ui/app/%28public%29/onboard/%5Btoken%5D/page.tsx#50-66) to call `/api/onboard` and handle 409 responses
  - Added conflict banner UI with status-aware messages
  - Changed "Create New Anyway" → "Contact Us" (mailto link)
  - Updated review screen with dynamic extraction banner
- **⚠️ Known issue:** TypeScript type for `conflictProperty` is missing [status](file:///Users/clawadmin/Antigravity%20Proj/ihouse-core/src/api/onboarding_router.py#551-647) field — there's a TS error that was not yet fixed when the session was interrupted
- **Size:** ~1097 lines total

### 4. [NOT MODIFIED] [package.json](file:///Users/clawadmin/Antigravity%20Proj/ihouse-core/ihouse-ui/package.json)
