## Database Migrations Applied

Four migrations were applied to `reykggmlcehswrxjviup` (Supabase project):

### Migration 1: `create_properties_and_channel_map` (20260313084640)
```sql
-- Created properties table + channel_map table
-- These may have existed before in some form — verify
```

### Migration 2: `allow_public_onboarding_inserts` (20260313093737)
```sql
-- RLS policies enabling anonymous inserts for public-onboard tenant
```

### Migration 3: `add_property_deduplication_constraints` (20260313103720)
```sql
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX idx_properties_tenant_source_url
ON properties (tenant_id, source_url)
WHERE source_url IS NOT NULL;

CREATE UNIQUE INDEX idx_channel_map_unique_mapping
ON channel_map (tenant_id, property_id, provider);
```

### Migration 4: `property_lifecycle_redesign` (20260313105847)
```sql
ALTER TABLE properties
  ADD COLUMN status TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pending'
    CHECK (status IN ('pending', 'approved', 'archived', 'rejected')),
  ADD COLUMN approved_at TIMESTAMPTZ,
  ADD COLUMN approved_by TEXT,
  ADD COLUMN archived_at TIMESTAMPTZ,
  ADD COLUMN archived_by TEXT;

CREATE TABLE tenant_property_config (
  tenant_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
  id_prefix TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'DOM'
    CHECK (id_prefix ~ '^[A-Z]{2,5}$'),
  next_seq INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 1
);

INSERT INTO tenant_property_config (tenant_id, id_prefix)
VALUES ('public-onboard', 'DOM');

-- RLS + index also added
```

