## What Was NOT Completed

1. **TypeScript type fix** — `conflictProperty` state is typed as `{ property_id: string; display_name: string; created_at: string }` but the API also returns [status](file:///Users/clawadmin/Antigravity%20Proj/ihouse-core/src/api/onboarding_router.py#551-647). The type needs [status](file:///Users/clawadmin/Antigravity%20Proj/ihouse-core/src/api/onboarding_router.py#551-647) added. There are 6 TS errors on this.

2. **Success screen update** — The success screen still says "has been created in our system" instead of "submitted for review". This was in progress when the session was stopped.

3. **Admin approval endpoints** — `POST /api/admin/properties/:id/approve` and `/reject` were designed but not created.

4. **Archive/unarchive endpoints** — Designed but not created.

5. **Hard delete test endpoint** — Designed but not created.

