## Quick Revert Instructions (if needed)

If the main agent decides to revert everything:

```sql
-- Revert migration 4
ALTER TABLE properties DROP COLUMN IF EXISTS status;
ALTER TABLE properties DROP COLUMN IF EXISTS approved_at;
ALTER TABLE properties DROP COLUMN IF EXISTS approved_by;
ALTER TABLE properties DROP COLUMN IF EXISTS archived_at;
ALTER TABLE properties DROP COLUMN IF EXISTS archived_by;
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS tenant_property_config;

-- Revert migration 3
DROP INDEX IF EXISTS idx_properties_tenant_source_url;
DROP INDEX IF EXISTS idx_channel_map_unique_mapping;

-- Clean test data
DELETE FROM channel_map WHERE tenant_id = 'public-onboard';
DELETE FROM properties WHERE tenant_id = 'public-onboard';
```

File reverts would need git — check `git status` and `git diff` in the ihouse-ui directory.
